methods.colorPaletteAlgorithm:
Gets the algorithm corresponding to the given name.

:param name: (java.lang.String) - case insensitive algorithm descriptor
:return: (io.deephaven.gui.color.ColorPaletteAlgorithms) algorithm corresponding to the given name
methods.colorPaletteAlgorithmNames:
Gets the names of the available ColorPaletteAlgorithms.

:return: (java.lang.String[]) array of the available ColorPaletteAlgorithms names
methods.getInitialColor:
Gets the algorithm's starting Color.

:return: (io.deephaven.gui.color.Color) algorithm's starting Color
methods.nextColor:
Gets the next Color after c in the algorithm.

:param c: (io.deephaven.gui.color.Color) - color
:return: (io.deephaven.gui.color.Color) result of plugging c in the algorithm
methods.valueOf:
Returns the enum constant of this type with the specified name.
The string must match exactly an identifier used to declare an
enum constant in this type.  (Extraneous whitespace characters are 
not permitted.)

:param name: (java.lang.String) - the name of the enum constant to be returned.
:return: (io.deephaven.gui.color.ColorPaletteAlgorithms) the enum constant with the specified name
methods.values:
Returns an array containing the constants of this enum type, in
the order they are declared.

:return: (io.deephaven.gui.color.ColorPaletteAlgorithms[]) an array containing the constants of this enum type, in the order they are declared
